<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Runetap | Official Site</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --black: #050508;
            --panel: #0d0d12;
            --border: #1e1e2e;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --dim: #777799;
            --runetap-main: #00d2ff; /* Runetap branding color */
            --warning-amber: #f4d03f;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

        body {
            background: var(--black);
            color: var(--white);
            font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        nav {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(5,5,8,0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        }

        .nav-logo {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--runetap-main);
            text-decoration: none;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 50vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 10rem 2rem 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .hero-title {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 10vw, 5rem);
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        section { padding: 4rem 2rem; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }

        .section-label {
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            letter-spacing: 0.3em;
            color: var(--dim);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            display: block;
            border-left: 3px solid var(--runetap-main);
            padding-left: 15px;
        }

        .content-panel {
            background: var(--panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            padding: 2.5rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
        }

        .download-btn {
            display: inline-block; 
            background: var(--runetap-main); 
            color: black; 
            padding: 15px 40px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            font-weight: bold; 
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }
        .download-btn:hover { 
            transform: scale(1.05);
            background: var(--white);
        }

        .back-link {
            display: block;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 3rem;
            color: var(--dim);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: 'Space Mono';
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        footer { text-align: center; padding: 4rem; opacity: 0.4; font-family: 'Space Mono'; font-size: 0.7rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav><a href="#" class="nav-logo">RUNETAP</a></nav>

<div class="hero">
    <p style="color:var(--runetap-main); font-family:'Space Mono'; margin-bottom: 10px; letter-spacing: 5px;">A PROJECT BY KILLSWITCH</p>
    <h1 class="hero-title">RUNE<span style="color:var(--runetap-main);">TAP</span></h1>
</div>

<section id="game-info">
    <span class="section-label">FILE_01: OVERVIEW</span>
    <div class="content-panel">
        <h2 style="font-family:'Space Mono'; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Standalone Experience.</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--dim); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">
            Runetap is an independent project developed from the ground up. Separate from other studio titles, this game focuses on core survival mechanics and precision gameplay.
        </p>
        
        <div style="background: #1a1a25; aspect-ratio: 16/9; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 2rem 0;">
            </div>

        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="https://github.com/dubiousgames/games/releases/download/update/RUNETAP.v1.8.6.zip" class="download-btn">
                DOWNLOAD RUNETAP.ZIP
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="safety-guide">
    <span class="section-label" style="border-color: var(--warning-amber);">LOG_02: INSTALLATION</span>
    <div class="content-panel" style="border-color: var(--warning-amber);">
        <h3 style="font-family:'Space Mono'; color: var(--warning-amber); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">SETUP INSTRUCTIONS</h3>
        <ul style="list-style: none; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--dim);">
            <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong style="color:var(--white);">1.</strong> Extract the .zip file to its own folder.</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 10px;"><strong style="color:var(--white);">2.</strong> Run <strong>Runetap.exe</strong>.</li>
            <li style="margin-bottom: 20px;"><strong style="color:var(--white);">3.</strong> If a Windows protection prompt appears, click <strong>"More Info"</strong> and then <strong>"Run Anyway"</strong>.</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-style: italic;">This prompt is a normal part of running independent software directly from the developer.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<a href="https://dubiousgames.github.io/" class="back-link">← BACK TO DUBIOUS GAMES HUB</a>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 DUBIOUS GAMES. DEVELOPED BY KILLSWITCH.</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
</body></html>
